Amina Barcham Bakhit (amụrụ na 14 Nọvemba 1990) bụ onye Sudan na-agba ọsọ n'etiti
Na 2012 Summer Olympics, ọ sonyere na mita 800 nke ụmụ nwanyị.
O ritere ọla edo na 2007 Pan Arab Games na 800 m na ọla nchara na 10,000 m na 2011 Pan Arab Games.
Bakhit nwalere norandrosterone na asọmpi na Sollentuna, Sweden na June 2009 ma mesịa nye ya mmachibido iwu afọ abụọ site na egwuregwu. Mmachibido iwu ahụ kwụsịrị na 16 Julaị 2011.
